OL,3,CNHS staff intimidated and fearful of
OL,4,Charassment, union claims
OL,6,FNHS staff are being harassed by
OL,7,Fmembers of the public filming them
OL,8,Fwith phones and threatening to post
OL,9,Ffootage online, according to new
OL,10,Fresearch.
OL,12,FA survey of thousands of UK health
OL,13,Fworkers revealed that one in seven
OL,14,Fhave experienced unwanted and
OL,15,Fintrusive filming or photography in
OL,16,Fthe past year, Unison said.
OL,18,FThe union said incidents are leaving
OL,19,Fstaff feeling intimidated and fearful.
