OL,3,CNHS staff intimidated and fearful of
OL,4,Charassment, union claims
OL,6,FExperiences have included people using
OL,7,Ftheir phones to film health workers on
OL,8,Fduty or giving emergency care as they
OL,9,Ftreat patients for cardiac arrests and
OL,10,Fthen that footage being livestreamed
OL,11,For put on social media platforms, the
OL,12,Fstudy revealed.
OL,14,FPhone cameras are also being as used
OL,15,Fas the digital equivalent of
OL,16,F"rubbernecking", said the union, with
OL,17,Fone member of the public brazenly
OL,18,Ffilming a victim of a car accident
OL,19,Fwith serious injuries despite pleas
OL,20,Ffrom staff to stop.
