OL,3,CNHS staff intimidated and fearful of
OL,4,Charassment, union claims
OL,6,FIncidents are occurring in hospitals,
OL,7,Fpatients' homes and even during
OL,8,Fmedical consultations, with the
OL,9,Ffootage being livestreamed to
OL,10,Frelatives who sometimes interrupt and
OL,11,Fdisagree with diagnoses being given by
OL,12,Fclinical staff, said Unison.
OL,14,FOne member of staff said: "Patients
OL,15,Fthink they can get their own way (and
OL,16,Fmake you do things you don't have to)
OL,17,Fby getting a phone out and filming
OL,18,Fjust to intimidate you."
