OL,6,FUnison general secretary Christina
OL,7,FMcAnea said: "Health workers must be
OL,8,Fable to do their jobs free from
OL,9,Fharassment, unwanted and intrusive
OL,10,Ffilming and associated threats of
OL,11,Fviolence.
OL,13,F"Their work is tough enough as it is,
OL,14,Fwithout people shoving phones in their
OL,15,Ffaces and putting them under a whole
OL,16,Fnew level of pressure.
