OL,3,CNHS staff intimidated and fearful of
OL,4,Charassment, union claims
OL,6,F"Harassing NHS workers through social
OL,7,Fmedia, or threatening to post material
OL,8,Fonline, is completely unacceptable.
OL,10,F"Employers and the Government must
OL,11,Ftake this issue seriously, provide
OL,12,Fsolid support and intervene properly,
OL,13,Fnot abandon staff to tackle the online
OL,14,Fbullies themselves.
OL,16,F"Employers should make it clear that
OL,17,Ffilming staff at work without consent
OL,18,Fis harassment and that they will come
OL,19,Fdown hard on anyone who indulges in
OL,20,Fthis kind of threatening anti-social
OL,21,Fbehaviour."
